Cops in Apel outside
Lebowakgomo in Limpopo are looking for 26-year-old Karel Nchabeleng.Nchabeleng is being sought for  questioning 
regarding a series of serious and violent crimes ranging from murder,
armed robbery to attempted murder.Police spokesperson 
Colonel  Moatshe Ngoepe  said Nchabeleng is also wanted for
questioning regarding  several other
